snippet.title: Dig Dug Revival (PC Dig Dug remake) (by Luca Carminati, LC-Games)
snippet.description:
Download Dig Dug Revival from https://lowcarb.itch.io.

This game is a homage to Dig Dug, an arcade game developed by Namco in 1982.

In this version, except the first one, the playfields are procedurally generated.

Author: Luca Carminati (lucacarminati1967@gmail.com).
